  <entry>
    <title>How to write Shell script</title>
    <link href="https://dtover.github.io/2020/07/17/How-to-write-Shell-script/"/>
    <id>https://dtover.github.io/2020/07/17/How-to-write-Shell-script/</id>
    <published>2020-07-17T11:18:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-01T12:09:03.321Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="How-to-write-Shell-script"><a href="#How-to-write-Shell-script" class="headerlink" title="How to write Shell script"></a>How to write Shell script</h4><p><em>Here you can get to know the basic grammar of shell quickly</em></p><h5 id="1-Shell-variable"><a href="#1-Shell-variable" class="headerlink" title="1. Shell variable"></a>1. Shell variable</h5><p><strong>Valid format of variable</strong> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">NAME</span><br><span class="line">LD_LIBTARY_PATH</span><br><span class="line">_var</span><br><span class="line">var2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><p><strong>How to use the variable</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var="this is a variable"</span><br><span class="line">echo $var</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">Set the var <span class="built_in">read</span> only</span></span><br><span class="line">readonly var</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;var&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">delete the var</span></span><br><span class="line">unset var</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>It’s a good habit to have a pair of brace</em></p><h4 id="2-Shell-string"><a href="#2-Shell-string" class="headerlink" title="2. Shell string"></a>2. Shell string</h4><p><strong>joint string</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var1="ruboob"</span><br><span class="line">var2='great'</span><br><span class="line">greeting="$&#123;var1&#125;,$&#123;var2&#125;"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Operation string</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">string="abcdefg"</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">get the length of the string</span></span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;#string&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">get the four chars of string start from index 1, Attention:  index start from 0</span></span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;string:1:4&#125; #get "unoo"</span><br><span class="line">var="This is a string"</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;string#*s&#125;    #s is a string</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;string##*s&#125;   #tring</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;string%s*&#125;    #This is a </span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;string%%s*&#125;   #Thi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Search the string</strong> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">string="abcdefghijkl"</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">print</span> the first index of char <span class="string">'i'</span></span></span><br><span class="line">echo `expr index "$&#123;string&#125; i"`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-Shell-array"><a href="#3-Shell-array" class="headerlink" title="3. Shell array"></a>3. Shell array</h3><p><strong>Declare an array</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#Attention : no comma inside</span><br><span class="line">array_name1&#x3D;(value0 value1 value2 value3)</span><br><span class="line">#or</span><br><span class="line">array_name2[0]&#x3D;value0</span><br><span class="line">array_name2[1]&#x3D;value1</span><br><span class="line">array_name2[2]&#x3D;value2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Operation array</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">array_value=$&#123;array_name1[n]&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">get all elements of the array</span></span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;array_name1[@]&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">get the length of the array</span></span><br><span class="line">length=$&#123;#array_name[@]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">length=$&#123;#array_name[*]&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">get the length of the first element of array</span></span><br><span class="line">length=$&#123;#array_name[0]&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-Shell-Comment"><a href="#4-Shell-Comment" class="headerlink" title="4. Shell Comment"></a>4. Shell Comment</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># This is a comment line</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:&lt;&lt;EOF</span><br><span class="line">This is a </span><br><span class="line">triple-line</span><br><span class="line">comment</span><br><span class="line">EOF</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>‘EOF’ here can be replaced by any other symbol (like ‘, !)</em></p><h3 id="5-Shell-parameter"><a href="#5-Shell-parameter" class="headerlink" title="5. Shell parameter"></a>5. Shell parameter</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ bash .&#x2F;shell.sh 1 2 3</span><br><span class="line">$0 : the file name of shell</span><br><span class="line">$1 : 1</span><br><span class="line">$2 : 2</span><br><span class="line">$3 : 3</span><br><span class="line">$# : 3 # the number the parameter</span><br><span class="line">$* : show all the parameters as a string</span><br><span class="line">$@ : some as $*</span><br><span class="line">$? : show the status of the last command</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-Shell-Operator"><a href="#6-Shell-Operator" class="headerlink" title="6. Shell Operator"></a>6. Shell Operator</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var&#x3D;&#96;expr 2 + 2&#96;</span><br><span class="line">var&#x3D;$(expr 2 + 2)</span><br><span class="line">var&#x3D;&#96;expr 2 \* 3&#96;</span><br><span class="line">a&#x3D;10</span><br><span class="line">b&#x3D;20</span><br><span class="line">if [ $a !&#x3D; $b -a $b -gt $(expr $a - $b) ];then</span><br><span class="line"> echo &quot;hi&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">string&#x3D;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">if [ -n &quot;$string&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">echo &quot;The length of the string is 0&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[[ &amp;&amp; || &gt; &lt; ]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h4 id=&quot;How-to-write-Shell-script&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#How-to-write-Shell-script&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;How to write Shell script&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;How to write Shell script&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Here you can get to know the basic grammar of shell quickly&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&quot;1-Shell-variable&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-Shell-variable&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1. Shell variable&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. Shell variable&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Valid format of variable&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;NAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;LD_LIBTARY_PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;_var&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;var2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
