    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="This-file-records-the-steps-to-install-deb-package-in-arch-linux"><a href="#This-file-records-the-steps-to-install-deb-package-in-arch-linux" class="headerlink" title="This file records the steps to install deb package in arch linux"></a>This file records the steps to install deb package in arch linux</h4><p><strong>1. Download Deb package</strong><br><strong>2. Extract with the following commands</strong></p><blockquote><p>ar x package.deb<br>xz -dk package.tar.zx<br>(<em>-d: Extract</em>)<br>(<em>-k: Keep file after extracting</em>)<br>pacman -U package.tar</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h4 id=&quot;This-file-records-the-steps-to-install-deb-package-in-arch-linux&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#This-file-records-the-steps-to-install-deb-package-in-arch-linux&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;This file records the steps to install deb package in arch linux&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;This file records the steps to install deb package in arch linux&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Download Deb package&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Extract with the following commands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ar x package.deb&lt;br&gt;xz -dk package.tar.zx&lt;br&gt;(&lt;em&gt;-d: Extract&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;br&gt;(&lt;em&gt;-k: Keep file after extracting&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;br&gt;pacman -U package.tar&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
