    <published>2020-04-28T09:09:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-01T12:09:51.061Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Yum-Commands"><a href="#Yum-Commands" class="headerlink" title="Yum Commands"></a>Yum Commands</h3><p><em>This file records some useful yum commands</em></p><p><strong>1. List all the package that can update:</strong>  </p><blockquote><p>yum check-update</p></blockquote><p><strong>2. Update all the software:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum update</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><p><strong>3. Install the package:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum install <package_name></p></blockquote><p><strong>4. Update the software:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum update <package_name></p></blockquote><p><strong>5. List all the package that can be installed:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum list</p></blockquote><p><strong>6. Delete the package:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum remove <package_name></p></blockquote><p><strong>7. Find the package:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum search <keyword></p></blockquote><p><strong>8. Clear storage:</strong></p><blockquote><p>yum clean packages<br>yum clean headers<br>yum clean oldheaders<br>yum clean yum clean all</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;Yum-Commands&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Yum-Commands&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Yum Commands&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Yum Commands&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This file records some useful yum commands&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. List all the package that can update:&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;yum check-update&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Update all the software:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;yum update&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
